This dataset is proprietary to the University School for Advanced Studies IUSS Pavia, Italy.
Data collection was conducted by the research team of the Laboratory of Neurolinguistics and Experimental Pragmatics (NEPLab) within the project “PROcessing MEtaphors: Neurochronometry, Acquisition and DEcay (PROMENADE)”, ERC CONSOLIDATOR GRANT: Grant agreement ID: 101045733 (principal investigator: Prof. Valentina Bambini).
Data and script usage is restricted to academic and non-commercial research upon appropriate attribution. 

Please, check the README.md file for further information concerning the study and the content of the dataset. 
For inquiries, contact: Dr. Federico Frau (federico.frau@iusspavia.it) and Dr. Paolo Canal (paolo.canal@iusspavia.it).